    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Guardian sphere.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When your delayed damage pool empties, you may as an immediate action redirect the damage you would take to augment or implant on your person or an innate gadget. The damage redirected this way is treated as untyped lethal damage, bypassing any damage reduction or hardness the augment or implant would possess otherwise.</p>\n<p><strong>Special:</strong> This overrides the normal rules for the delayed damage pool which states that you cannot further redirect damage from the delayed damage pool.</p>\n",
